  "body": "# Bug Report\r\n\r\n## Description\r\nObserved that scrolling can get stuck for a few seconds at a time while messages are arriving. These may impact the user after restoring an account for over 20+ minutes as messages load.\r\n\r\n\r\nhttps://user-images.githubusercontent.com/50769329/232924100-bf2da5ab-224b-4536-b9bd-db57a989a348.mp4\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nhttps://user-images.githubusercontent.com/50769329/232923281-5fda6501-ea93-4124-8e7b-4837400f0ca4.mp4\r\n\r\n\r\n## Steps to reproduce\r\n\r\nRestore account with community that has significant chat history\r\nAttempt to scroll / navigate while the history requests are still loading messages\r\n\r\n#### Expected behavior\r\n\r\n#### Actual behavior\r\nScrolling can get stuck as messages arrive or cause flicker\r\n\r\n### Additional Information\r\n\r\n- Status desktop version: https://ci.status.im/job/status-desktop/job/branches/job/macos/job/aarch64/job/package/job/PR-10292/3/ (found during #10292 )\r\n- Operating System: Mac\r\n\r\n",
